General.Name: Urstadt Biddle Properties Inc
General.Description: Urstadt Biddle Properties Inc. is a self-administered equity real estate investment trust which owns or has equity interests in 77 properties containing approximately 5.3 million square feet of space. Listed on the New York Stock Exchange since 1970, it provides investors with a means of participating in ownership of income-producing properties. It has paid 213 consecutive quarters of uninterrupted dividends to its shareholders since its inception. As of August 18, 2023, Urstadt Biddle Properties Inc. operates as a subsidiary of Regency Centers Corporation.
